--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
version 1.17.0.3  |  2015-06-19  |  Voice System Package 4.36 RC7
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHG Require xRX300 FW version 2.0.0.
CHG Increased the default number of channels to 16. [VOICECPE_SW-922]
NEW Fill the new field BurstNumber in the jitter buffer statistics report IOCTL
    if the firmware version provides this value. [VOICECPE_SW-887]
CHG New configuration option to disable the automatic connection between data
    channels which are connected to the same Phone, DECT or PCM module.
    The option --disable-automatic-datachannel-mapping disables the automatic
    mapping which is enabled by default. When the automatic mapping is disabled
    the IOCTLs IFX_TAPI_MAP_DATA_ADD and IFX_TAPI_MAP_DATA_REMOVE can be used
    to create data channel to data channel mappings. This allows to create
    direct data channel connections without using a Phone, DECT or PCM module.
    [VOICECPE_SW-953]
CHG Improved return codes for the connection IOCTLs:
    - IFX_TAPI_MAP_PHONE_ADD, IFX_TAPI_MAP_PHONE_REMOVE
    - IFX_TAPI_MAP_DATA_ADD, IFX_TAPI_MAP_DATA_REMOVE
    - IFX_TAPI_MAP_PCM_ADD, IFX_TAPI_MAP_PCM_REMOVE
    - IFX_TAPI_MAP_DECT_ADD, IFX_TAPI_MAP_DECT_REMOVE [VOICECPE_SW-954]

