    --disable-slic the driver will not initialise the SmartSLIC. Note that not
    all services based on the SLIC are blocked in the driver. [VOICECPE_SW-798]
FIX Resolved problem that no more than one metering burst could be sent after
    setting the linefeed to active. [VOICECPE_SW-671]
FIX Reset the flag preventing clock scaling after FW boot has completed.
    [VOICECPE_SW-924]
CHG Extend the tone generator code to support up to 28 UTGs depending on the FW
    capabilities. [VOICECPE_SW-922]
CHG Extend the connection handling to support up to 14 COD/SIG modules depending
    on the FW capabilities. [VOICECPE_SW-922]

